result.original_title: Schick deine Frau nicht nach Italien
result.title: Do Not Send Your Wife to Italy
result.overview: Manuela, Lizzie and Sabine are annoyed by their husbands. So they decide to go to Italy where they hope to meet some nice men.

result.title: A Francesa e o Amor
result.overview: The seven stages in the life of the modern Frenchwomen are disclosed by seven directors in a witty way: 1 - Childhood, 2 - Adolescence, 3 - Virginity, 4 - Marriage, 5 - Adultery, 6 - Divorce, 7 - The Single Woman.
